text: Hypseleotris galii, the firetail gudgeon, is a species of gudgeon native to eastern Australia, where it is found in freshwater streams. Gale's carp- gudgeon is an alternate common name. ==References== ==External links== * Fishes of Australia : Hypseleotris galii galii Category:Freshwater fish of Australia firetail gudgeon
title: Hypseleotris galii
